    "description": "<strong>You pass by the attic. You hear a knock.</strong><br>Aside from the floorboards creaking under your feet. It's silent in here.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047180/extras/7883b2cf143e72ad036d9043ec70a70b.poster.avif?t=1726587705\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047180/extras/7883b2cf143e72ad036d9043ec70a70b.webm?t=1726587705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047180/extras/7883b2cf143e72ad036d9043ec70a70b.mp4?t=1726587705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>What's there by the window?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047180/extras/87b0295986ea93dcdbed851f7e603559.poster.avif?t=1726587705\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047180/extras/87b0295986ea93dcdbed851f7e603559.webm?t=1726587705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047180/extras/87b0295986ea93dcdbed851f7e603559.mp4?t=1726587705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There is a carved circle in the window sill.<br>And a tiny glass ball in the middle of it.<br>It's blue, clean from dust.<br>Charming, like a little piece of sky that fell.<br>...Or was it offered?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047180/extras/0a0ed6ab5631e5647c3969257d24668f.poster.avif?t=1726587705\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047180/extras/0a0ed6ab5631e5647c3969257d24668f.webm?t=1726587705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047180/extras/0a0ed6ab5631e5647c3969257d24668f.mp4?t=1726587705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Who leaves marbles by the attics' window?<br>Are you truly alone in this house?<br>Find out the origins of little treasures left on the windowsill. Feed your obsessive paranoia or befriend...some kind of creature?<br><br><strong>Enter the Attic.</strong><br><br>The Attic is a Visual Novel and Walking Simulator style game with multiple endings.<br>You, the main character, live alone in this old house. When one day you hear a knock in your attic. While entering it you find little blue marble at the windowsill.<br>The outcome of this story is up to you.<br>Do you find the whole ordeal of blue marbles at the attic whimsical?...or threatening?<br><br>This game is a love letter to the classical horror stories about old haunted houses, basements and ofcourse attics. Psychological horror inspired by author's experience with OCD-like symptoms and intrusive thoughts.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047180/extras/0c27d48ae3fcbe480899a76b5b3bd8c4.avif?t=1726587705\" width=690 height=388 /></span>",
